Package clientSide.entities

Interface StudentCloning

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BarClientProxy, TableClientProxy
    public interface StudentCloning
    Student cloning. It specifies his own attributes. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
